{"id": 2240, "genre": 1001, "title": "买到了想差评的商品or服务，你最后会为啥放弃讨回公道？", "description": "迫于物理障碍和心理压力，不得不扮演一个当代老好人。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2042, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180321114751lWfXvPM1UdCE36sz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-23T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 272642, "content": "做生意都不容易，以后避开就好了。钱当喂狗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243331}, {"id": 282370, "content": "操作繁琐，浪费时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347784}, {"id": 272645, "content": "想想其实大家都挺不容易的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293646}, {"id": 272646, "content": "该死de移动，绑定我最低消费一直退不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294669}, {"id": 273158, "content": "是准备讨回公道的，但是客服那五块钱收买了我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238577}, {"id": 272650, "content": "怕烦 节约时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1170915}, {"id": 275210, "content": "还能忍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311283}, {"id": 272653, "content": "我基本不会品论，偶尔给个差评，商家就会不耐起烦的给你打电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239451}, {"id": 272654, "content": "买的东西很便宜 怕麻烦又有虚荣心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294782}, {"id": 272655, "content": "大家都不容易，不想互相伤害", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 395662}, {"id": 277519, "content": "懒癌晚期患者", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324866}, {"id": 272656, "content": "从来没有，每次必须维护自己的权益。希望维护途径更多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017784}, {"id": 272659, "content": "不想接到卖家电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 272661, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285278}, {"id": 272921, "content": "我一般都是退货 之前买了小米手机 收到是坏的 不给退钱只能换货帮我修 我就说我要投诉 还是拖最后态度坚决给我退钱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296673}, {"id": 272666, "content": "有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637660}, {"id": 273182, "content": "太忙，太懒没退货", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249991}, {"id": 273440, "content": "懒啊，还有价值决定", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299180}, {"id": 276008, "content": "怕麻烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295160}, {"id": 272937, "content": "怕被电话信息轰炸！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296926}, {"id": 272691, "content": "并不会放弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 273459, "content": "退货不赔邮费，最后凑合着用吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299347}, {"id": 272692, "content": "并不会放弃，我用的号码是虚拟的地址是驿站", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 272694, "content": "就算真的举报或者差评了，作用也不大，商家不会真正地改正。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294982}, {"id": 272695, "content": "所谓的意见会换来客服无数次的电话骚扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289519}, {"id": 272696, "content": "上一次打差评买家给我打了一堆电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1255316}, {"id": 272699, "content": "在收集证据的过程中，气消了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844272}, {"id": 272702, "content": "我觉得记几时间比较值钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 273214, "content": "积极解决问题，态度诚恳，大家都不容易啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271097}, {"id": 272447, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 804, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932193}, {"id": 272703, "content": "从未放弃追追讨公道！╯^╰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273278}, {"id": 272448, "content": "担心被贴上“刺头”“事儿逼”的标签，被看成斤斤计较心胸狭窄没有容人的肚量，道德高地如此寒冷，当圣人就得喝雪水，心凉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236388}, {"id": 272449, "content": "找熟人买的，不好意思还回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919463}, {"id": 272450, "content": "我能做到的讨回公道的方法就是给差评，退都懒得退，麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853320}, {"id": 272706, "content": "卖家淘宝联系我，短信联系我，电话联系我，怕了怕了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295046}, {"id": 272451, "content": "一直买运费险，不好的产品能退都退。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289663}, {"id": 272707, "content": "都不容易", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295061}, {"id": 272452, "content": "怕网红粉丝怼", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128178}, {"id": 272708, "content": "麻烦", "image": "img/option/option/20180324180619e3aPX5QonUsxmVyp", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295064}, {"id": 272709, "content": "我也感觉每次出现问题遇见的卖家态度都还挺好的，可能也有前期筛选的原因", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219386}, {"id": 272454, "content": "投诉了基本也没用，永远态度很好永远解决不了不问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283578}, {"id": 272455, "content": "担心对方报复，毕竟个人信息都在他们手里", "image": null, "praise_count": 281, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 272711, "content": "当发现维护不了自己的权益时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295089}, {"id": 272456, "content": "永无止境的维权之路，荆棘密布、险象环生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292664}, {"id": 272457, "content": "让自己花钱买教训的就懒得退了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278548}, {"id": 272713, "content": "麻烦而价值不大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422133}, {"id": 272459, "content": "给差评要被卖家找麻烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206203}, {"id": 272460, "content": "昨天刚和12315联系。店大欺客，投诉无用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291683}, {"id": 272716, "content": "怕惹事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295148}, {"id": 272461, "content": "中评后客服没完没了的电话/信息，然后果断改成差评！", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269691}]}